graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Dashboard Pod"
        direction TB
        OAuthProxy[oauth-proxy container<br/>OpenShift OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        Backend[odh-dashboard container<br/>Fastify Backend API<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
        Frontend[React Frontend SPA<br/>PatternFly UI]
        K8sClient[Kubernetes Client<br/>@kubernetes/client-node]

        OAuthProxy -->|proxies auth| Backend
        Backend -->|serves static| Frontend
        Backend -->|uses| K8sClient
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resource Definitions Watched"
        OdhApp[OdhApplication<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        OdhConfig[OdhDashboardConfig<br/>opendatahub.io/v1alpha]
        OdhDoc[OdhDocument<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        QuickStart[OdhQuickStart<br/>console.openshift.io/v1]
        AccelProfile[AcceleratorProfile<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        Notebook[Notebook<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        InferenceService[InferenceService<br/>serving.kserve.io]
        ModelRegistry[ModelRegistry<br/>modelregistry.opendatahub.io]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        OSAuth[OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTP]
        ImageRegistry[OpenShift Image Registry<br/>5000/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    subgraph "Internal ODH Components"
        NotebookController[Notebook Controller]
        KServeController[KServe Controller]
        ModelRegComponent[Model Registry]
        DSCOperator[Data Science Cluster Operator]
        Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines]
    end

    User[User Browser] -->|HTTPS/443<br/>OAuth flow| OAuthProxy
    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates via| OSAuth
    K8sClient -->|HTTPS/6443<br/>CRUD operations| K8sAPI
    Backend -->|HTTP/9092<br/>metrics queries| Prometheus
    Backend -->|HTTPS/5000<br/>image metadata| ImageRegistry

    K8sAPI -->|watches/manages| OdhApp
    K8sAPI -->|watches/manages| OdhConfig
    K8sAPI -->|watches/manages| OdhDoc
    K8sAPI -->|watches/manages| QuickStart
    K8sAPI -->|watches/manages| AccelProfile
    K8sAPI -->|watches/manages| Notebook
    K8sAPI -->|watches/manages| InferenceService
    K8sAPI -->|watches/manages| ModelRegistry

    Backend -.->|integrates| NotebookController
    Backend -.->|integrates| KServeController
    Backend -.->|integrates| ModelRegComponent
    Backend -.->|integrates| DSCOperator
    Backend -.->|integrates| Pipelines

